title: Presidential Nomination Sent to the Senate | whitehouse.gov
content:
The White House
Office of the Press Secretary


For Immediate Release
June 23, 2014

 



Presidential Nomination Sent to the Senate




NOMINATION SENT TO THE SENATE:
Carolyn Watts Colvin, of Maryland, to be Commissioner of Social Security for the term expiring January 19, 2019, vice Michael J. Astrue, resigned.
